## Objetivo
An aviation company is conducting a raffle for tickets to travel to various places in the world. To participate you must register with the phrase hidden in this QRcode

QR code file

[https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FtJU4aNBmf_BYiThRotQ5z9zrSrWgFHM/view?usp=sharing](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FtJU4aNBmf_BYiThRotQ5z9zrSrWgFHM/view?usp=sharing)
